room_title: Escape room "The Attic" by The Ultimate Escape Rooms in Ventura
room_description:
When you were a child, your home felt like a secure and nurturing heaven from a dark and dangerous world. Except for the attic. Your parents warned you never to go up there.
You should have listened to them and stayed away. But the mystery drove you back and now you're trapped. Can you escape before you're forced to face horrible truths of your family?
